Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:05.35,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学的睫毛很美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:11.64,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还会乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.30,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,毕竟一直在练 这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:26.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我的朋友…好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.10,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,话说 明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:34.59,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你最近总是盯着我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:39.89,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真希望时间就此停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:43.65,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我们对彼此还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:47.35,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,可这是为什么呢？我已心悦于你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,开始的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:01:03.98,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(明日酱的水手服)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:07.56,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,陌生的景色闪耀起光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:11.29,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,是因为你呼唤了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:15.10,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我不要做同学 想当你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.87,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我暗自思念你已久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:26.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我想更加了解你 想让你更加了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:30.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,铃声打断了谈话 夕阳染红了你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.31,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不愿说出＂再见＂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:38.03,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真希望时间就此停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:41.78,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我们对彼此还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.52,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,可这是为什么呢？我已心悦于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.34,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,开始的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:53.00,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,用力挥手的你是如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:56.78,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,让我流连忘返
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:00.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,可这是为什么呢？我已心悦于你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.55,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,闪耀的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.00,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(第六集 明天不是不上课吗)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.06,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,接下来播报全国的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.77,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,从近畿地区到关东的持续降水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.63,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明早将会转晴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.69,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,预计全国范围都会是晴天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.11,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,下个周末我要请朋友来家里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,几个 几个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.14,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.04,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我还没胆子请那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.85,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,是叫江利花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.65,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,那个一眼就看穿你很有意思的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.40,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 得把房间打扫干净才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.30,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,等一下 饭已经做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.54,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,等下再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.74,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,一周前的我充满了自信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.23,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(周一)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:58.14,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次打算请同龄人来家里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.73,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(周二 语文 体育)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.96,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,怎样才能让她答应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.74,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(周三)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,在学校又不是不能聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.25,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(周三 周四)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.97,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,要玩也可以在课间玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.54,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,话说 明日同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.12,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我像这样纠结来纠结去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.72,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,时间转眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.61,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(周五)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:26.97,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,话说 明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:30.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你最近总是盯着我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.79,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,没…没盯着你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.97,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,骗人 现在不就盯着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.37,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,有什么难以启齿的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:45.10,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明…明天周六 不是不上课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.18,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯…为什么这么拘谨？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,就是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:58.10,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,漏…漏雨的房子 你怎么看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.23,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:03.13,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,肯定得补好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,在房子里我可不想被淋湿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.21,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,就…就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.95,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 我一直想知道你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.81,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.99,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,得把漏雨的地方补上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.36,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,否则没法请她来家里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:25.99,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,话说 明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.25,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我等下要去图书室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:32.25,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你要一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.25,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(图书室)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.49,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(大钓特钓！最新指南 钓鱼入门)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:38.72,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还在盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.86,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,原因明显没那么简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.17,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你看的书好像很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你钓过鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.36,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,钓过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.24,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,钓过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.51,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 在家附近的湖里钓过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.21,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,但不是书上那种帅气的钓法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.86,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,用的是弹性很好的树枝和缝纫机线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.95,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,鱼饵是吃剩下的鱿鱼须
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.31,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,自己做钓具？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.13,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不过我钓上来的全是小龙虾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.75,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,从来没钓到过鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.98,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,这种时候我就会光着脚下水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.11,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,光着脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.60,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,然后我把鱼赶到一起 花绪就用网…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.02,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.25,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我早就想这样玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.53,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.47,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:31.98,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:38.86,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,-如果你方便 那个… -对啊 不是把人请到家里就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.50,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,一起去钓鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.08,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你看明天行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.32,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明天周六 不是不上课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.09,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你一直盯着我看 难道是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.15,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.27,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.42,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,跟朋友相约在周末见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.69,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:47.00,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,(明日酱的水手服)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还有这么个地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.79,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,碰头地点选得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.55,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我竟然早到了足足一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.56,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.90,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学会是什么反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,要不要先适应一下水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我可不想在明日同学面前丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.85,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,要是让妈妈看见了 非得骂死我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.09,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不好 一不小心就兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.44,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,妈妈做的裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.10,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,今天是第一次穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.37,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,毕竟是去见木崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.41,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,怎么能穿平时穿的运动服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.07,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.41,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.76,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.01,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:39.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.36,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你的游泳技术真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.60,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.09,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学也穿了能下水的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.63,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,跟泳装比还是差了点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.86,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学 今天请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.26,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.08,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我找人问了容易钓到鱼的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.94,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,只不过要走上一截
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:05.84,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我们过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.33,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你的装备好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.93,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,刚买没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.56,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不过一直没机会钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.13,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,今天是第一次用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,所以我特别期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.96,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 鱼竿是很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.64,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不过我意思是你浑身上下都很酷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.94,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.15,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.38,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,愿木崎同学今天能钓到大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.97,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,在这里绝对能钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.37,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好 我也来做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.80,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你就用那东西钓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.59,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,鱼竿都不用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.68,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 用米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.82,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,用这个可以钓到小鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.80,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我在这边试试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.78,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.60,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,这鱼叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.17,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你等等 我查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.91,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,拉…拉氏鱥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.61,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小鱥 这名字好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.30,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.47,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,用那么简陋的钓具都能钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.56,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我也不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.92,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,鱼是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:49.82,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,绝对有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.31,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,又是小鱥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.87,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,可我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.41,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,毕竟你用的是不能吃的饵 很难钓的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.15,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,可我只有这种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.65,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,要不试试刚才鸟抓鱼的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.34,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过太远了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.84,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,感觉鱼饵抛太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.67,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,停一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.11,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,抛竿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.92,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真厉害 正正好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.79,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好像拉不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.57,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我游过去取下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.02,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,那还不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.83,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我绕个角度 看看能不能取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.44,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.51,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,居然因为这点小事就这么兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.07,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不过 我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.60,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,又挂上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.21,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.46,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,这是上钩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:33.83,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.64,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,水灌进来了 想回都回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.85,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.41,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学 鱼上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:47.77,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,快来帮我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.93,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.01,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.12,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.01,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你先帮我拿着 我把涉水裤脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:01.51,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:13.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学 我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.39,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:23.19,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,原来鱼的力气这么大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.47,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,怎样才能钓上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.54,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学 用这个装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.27,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.98,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.27,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.65,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,来 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.08,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,太厉害了 是真的鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.38,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,-木崎同学看上去好开心 -原来摸着是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.33,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,背上的斑点太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不过一直困着它也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.32,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.16,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,游走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.02,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,接下来我们要玩水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.29,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我说 木崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.35,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,今天玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.19,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.36,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学 换的衣服带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.00,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,带了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,有能换衣服的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.29,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还有洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.24,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,去那边的树荫就没人能看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.13,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,说…说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.61,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,马上就到我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:41.96,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.05,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,顺势就去明日同学家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.20,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,而且为的是换衣服和上厕所…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:49.72,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,花绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.78,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,花绪 木崎同学来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.04,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小号明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.55,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:04.04,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,姐姐带朋友来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.67,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,在湖那边看见的红屋顶房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.59,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,原来是你家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.49,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好大一片款冬叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.46,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,要不要拿来煮了吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.24,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不是当伞用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:26.85,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:29.27,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你就是大美女木崎同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:32.24,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 确实很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.95,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,别这样描述我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.37,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,今天冒昧来访…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:44.33,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,妈妈 木崎同学可厉害了 钓到了大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:45.86,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.89,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,是雄白点鲑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:51.08,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,-是吧 我也大吃一惊 -我也要看 我也要看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:51.95,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.87,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:02.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好 那你们两个先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:05.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,看来玩得挺欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.44,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,江利花 洗手间在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.20,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.51,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,花绪 去给客人拿浴巾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:13.88,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.64,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,江利花姐姐 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.76,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学的妈妈人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.14,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.14,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.75,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,那你们慢慢洗咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:27.73,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.06,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,浴巾好香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.40,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,在别人家脱光有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.62,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,那个 明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.03,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你先进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.46,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,她们两个好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,刚见面就直接叫你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.96,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,怎么称呼有这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.18,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我以前也没怎么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.50,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,但听见她们这样叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.07,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我就非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.56,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,非常羡慕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.27,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学 毫不犹豫就脱光了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.54,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你的皮肤好白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.39,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.43,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,没冲进眼睛里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.53,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.62,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,海绵擦着不疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.42,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.69,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我轻点擦 不能擦红了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:25.20,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.31,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,谢谢 换我给你冲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:33.26,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,不用 你先出去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,等你换好我就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.53,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.66,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,花绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.66,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,带木崎同学去房间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.69,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,顺便让妈妈把点心也拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.74,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,用过的浴巾直接放进洗衣机就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:52.86,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.30,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学真是无微不至
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.32,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,她在家里就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.22,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,自己的头发都没吹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.83,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.02,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.21,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:13.16,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,真羡慕你 姐姐总是这样细心地给你吹头发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:16.01,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 但不会用梳子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.65,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,都是用手指捋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.31,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,姐姐跟平时不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.58,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,现在在使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.95,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,花绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,用不着老老实实全说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.15,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我问你 花绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.22,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你喜欢明日同学…喜欢你姐姐哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.10,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,跟我说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.51,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,举止也很像明日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.99,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,别乱说 别乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:43.45,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小路 我拿饮料来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.76,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,开下门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.84,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,给你 点心和咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.84,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,妈妈 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.01,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.13,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,拍屁股声音很大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.46,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,花绪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.96,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,木崎同学又不爱听这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.17,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,可是姐姐会这样干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.47,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,为什么要这么干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.55,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,是为了逗笑刚出生的花绪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.81,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,她还干过很多丢脸的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:20.79,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.60,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:23.64,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.37,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,看啊 像是这张…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.48,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:36.35,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,我还想表现出帅气的一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.63,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,今天招待不周 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:48.63,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,没有 不仅请我喝了那么好喝的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.92,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,还开车送我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.52,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,已经很周到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.67,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,欢迎再来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:57.77,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.40,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,明日同学 学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.28,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯 学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:26.75,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小路同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:28.47,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小路同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.70,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,从今天起 我就叫你小路同学了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:34.75,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:39.13,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,你就叫我江利花吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.47,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:52.33,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小路 睡觉的时候小心别感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.22,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:19.75,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,走在冒险般的回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:25.30,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,只要有你 一切皆可乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:30.67,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,随心决定 轻松地迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:35.21,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,有朝一日 终将回到归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:45.89,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,啊 回荡的话语 啊 随风而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:54.96,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,啊 鸟儿也要歌唱 聚集同伴之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:23:04.84,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,傍晚的天空飘着飞机云 回荡着我们的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:14.89,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,每天就像画画一样 涂下一层层色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:25.08,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,想必此时此刻的回忆最是光彩夺目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:35.71,BDSPEC_ZHO,,0,0,0,,小心翼翼地抱在怀里 进入梦乡
